'''''Love in the Time of Black Tide''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Amphoreus]] in the chapter [[Amphoreus Annals]].

==Steps==
# Head to the rooftop to join the fun
# Listen to Aelius' troubles
# Receive the bad news with Aelius
# Ask Chartonus about Nympha's whereabouts
# Ask Kyros about Nympha's whereabouts
# Ask Theodoros about Nympha's whereabouts
# Go to the Marmoreal Palace and look for Nympha
# Rewind to the past and find where Nympha was imprisoned
# Witness Aelius' revelation
# Return to the market and find Nympha
# Head to the Dromas Workshop and bid farewell to these two

