:'''Kyros:''' It's the kind of order that you normally only see at wedding banquets... So is Nympha getting married!?
:Standing off to one side, Aelius can barely stay on his feet. He nearly drops to his knees &mdash; but luckily you're there to catch him.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Aelius, be strong.
